   "source": [
    "# Fitting a 3D Background Model to NASA TESS data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 304,
   "id": "1c89f897-8c6a-4cf5-b9b9-e637ef8b6ccf",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "from astropy.io import fits"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 305,
   "id": "a8029af7-92e3-43d7-a6ef-7440b82302a8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "hdulist = fits.open('data/kepler-10_in_TESS.fits')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 306,
   "id": "8f7a3d45-fbad-4a0c-acb2-2bf76d62e79c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "attrs = ['time', 'flux', 'flux_err', 'quality', 'pos_corr1', 'pos_corr2']\n",
    "d = {attr:hdulist[1].data[attr] for attr in attrs}\n",
    "d['quality'] = (d['quality'] & 175) == 0\n",
    "d['quality'] &= np.isfinite(d['flux']).all(axis=(1, 2)) \n",
    "d['quality'] &= np.isfinite(d['flux_err']).all(axis=(1, 2)) \n",
    "d['pipeline_mask'] = hdulist[2].data"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 307,
   "id": "c3057aba-38c6-4ab0-90dd-b3f1b877ee9f",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 308,
   "id": "6648dba8-fc6e-45d9-a3fe-b3052409add8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[Text(0.5, 0, 'Column'),\n",
       " Text(0, 0.5, 'Row'),\n",
       " Text(0.5, 1.0, 'Kepler-10 as seen by TESS')]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 308,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [

      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "ax.imshow(d['flux'][0], vmin=0, vmax=1000, origin='lower')\n",
    "ax.set(xlabel='Column', ylabel='Row', title='Kepler-10 as seen by TESS')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 309,
   "id": "86d45c92-466c-4f2c-a760-c2479a7481ea",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "shape = d['flux'].shape"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 310,
   "id": "26fd9b15-841c-44f7-8999-7746889f8c85",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "(1241, 20, 21)"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 310,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "shape"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 311,
   "id": "253c3daf-064c-4d67-b257-979485f5ff68",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "R, C = np.mgrid[:shape[1], :shape[2]]\n",
    "R = R.astype(float) - R.mean()\n",
    "C = C.astype(float) - C.mean()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 312,
   "id": "1e539a73-b13b-4eff-9c73-e0376a3b5dd5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from lamatrix import Fixed, Polynomial, Constant"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 313,
   "id": "cb9a0217-db6c-44f3-b2be-b660a44c23b3",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "p1 = Polynomial('r', 1)\n",
    "p2 = Polynomial('c', 1)\n",
    "p = p1 + p2 + p1 * p2 + Constant()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 314,
   "id": "76054c26-ec7a-4a2f-ad26-206c982afd27",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "mean_frame = d['flux'][630:660].mean(axis=0)\n",
    "mean_frame -= np.median(mean_frame)\n",
    "\n",
    "p.fit(data=mean_frame, mask=mean_frame < 50, r=R, c=C)\n",
    "mean_frame -= p.evaluate(r=R, c=C)\n",
    "\n",
    "dmean_frame1, dmean_frame2 = np.gradient(mean_frame)\n",
    "f = np.asarray([dmean_frame1, dmean_frame2]).transpose([1, 2, 0])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 315,
   "id": "c53f2cef-38cf-429c-878f-bc713fdb1ff4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x31dd9d760>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 315,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x300 with 3 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(10, 3), sharey=True)\n",
    "axs[0].imshow(mean_frame, vmin=-100, vmax=100)\n",
    "axs[1].imshow(dmean_frame1, vmin=-100, vmax=100, cmap='coolwarm')\n",
    "axs[2].imshow(dmean_frame2, vmin=-100, vmax=100, cmap='coolwarm')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 316,
   "id": "c7d111a9-c7fb-4dc6-a4a1-58a7e2e42e6c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "p =  p1 + p2 + p1 * p2 + Constant() + Fixed('f', 2)\n",
    "p.fit(data=d['flux'][0] - mean_frame, errors=d['flux_err'][0], c=C, r=R, f=f)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 317,
   "id": "8c399a04-f6ed-48c5-826f-220b4e6536cb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "JointModel\n",
       "\tPolynomial(r)[n, 1]\n",
       "\tPolynomial(c)[n, 1]\n",
       "\tCrosstermModel(r, c)[n, 1]\n",
       "\tConstant()[n, 1]\n",
       "\tFixed(f)[n, 2]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 317,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "p"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 318,
   "id": "8f0dcfe0-55e4-4dd5-a44b-bbc154009840",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "Fixed(f)[n, 2]"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 318,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "p[-1]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 319,
   "id": "9f732828-cbdf-4fa9-812c-0be7ebba8e24",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "array([-0.01852726,  0.01152998])"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 319,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "p[-1].posteriors.mean"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 320,
   "id": "04a18d81-601a-4b9c-9e91-381c88f16f9d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x31da4fc10>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 320,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 700x300 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(7, 3), sharey=True)\n",
    "axs[0].imshow(d['flux'][0] - np.nanmedian(d['flux'][0]), vmin=-100, vmax=100)\n",
    "axs[1].imshow(d['flux'][0] - p[:-1].evaluate(c=C, r=R, f=f), vmin=-100, vmax=100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 321,
   "id": "c65723cc-51dd-4405-9226-d90018b64e82",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "bkg, model = np.zeros((2, *shape), float)\n",
    "shift, shift_err = np.zeros((2, shape[0], 2))\n",
    "for idx in range(shape[0]):\n",
    "    p.fit(data=d['flux'][idx] - mean_frame, errors=d['flux_err'][idx], c=C, r=R, f=f)\n",
    "    model[idx] = p.evaluate(c=C, r=R, f=f)\n",
    "    bkg[idx] = p[:-1].evaluate(c=C, r=R, f=f)\n",
    "    shift[idx], shift_err[idx] = p[-1].posteriors.mean, p[-1].posteriors.std"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 322,
   "id": "62349d20-d86b-4539-93fd-df8c4218f409",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<ErrorbarContainer object of 3 artists>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 322,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.errorbar(d['time'], shift[:, 0], shift_err[:, 0], ls='', c='r')\n",
    "plt.errorbar(d['time'], shift[:, 1], shift_err[:, 1], ls='', c='b')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 360,
   "id": "053fd1b9-4175-4204-8a10-ab56e117044c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "chi2 = (1/(shape[0])) * np.sum((d['flux'] - model - mean_frame)**2/(d['flux_err'])**2, axis=0)\n",
    "bad_pixels = chi2 > 500"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 361,
   "id": "906bc56a-de59-4e06-aa00-4fb012bdef2b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x320df2460>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 361,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.imshow(chi2 > 500)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 362,
   "id": "5d85837a-585a-42ac-87ad-8fe9f9eea6d9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<ErrorbarContainer object of 3 artists>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 362,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "bkg, model = np.zeros((2, *shape), float)\n",
    "shift, shift_err = np.zeros((2, shape[0], 2))\n",
    "for idx in range(shape[0]):\n",
    "    p.fit(data=d['flux'][idx] - mean_frame, errors=d['flux_err'][idx], c=C, r=R, f=f, mask=~bad_pixels)\n",
    "    model[idx] = p.evaluate(c=C, r=R, f=f)\n",
    "    bkg[idx] = p[:-1].evaluate(c=C, r=R, f=f)\n",
    "    shift[idx], shift_err[idx] = p[-1].posteriors.mean, p[-1].posteriors.std\n",
    "plt.errorbar(d['time'], shift[:, 0], shift_err[:, 0], ls='', c='r')\n",
    "plt.errorbar(d['time'], shift[:, 1], shift_err[:, 1], ls='', c='b')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 363,
   "id": "3e232995-6f48-4666-bf71-6749174159ed",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "r = np.gradient(np.hypot(*(shift - np.median(shift, axis=0)).T), d['time'])\n",
    "bad_cadences = np.where(r > 0.5)[0] + 1\n",
    "k = np.ones(shape[0], bool)\n",
    "k[bad_cadences] = False"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 364,
   "id": "75494a3c-ad19-4d83-8455-a767747839de",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "aper = np.zeros(shape[1:], bool)\n",
    "aper[9:12, 9:12] = True"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 365,
   "id": "e101d4b0-ca6f-462f-85b4-9816277517b1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "c = ((shift[:, 0, None, None] * f[None, :, :, 0]) + (shift[:, 1, None, None] * f[None, :, :, 1]))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 366,
   "id": "2744a662-af47-4d54-9eb7-b320be801e5d",
   "metadata": {},

   ],
   "source": [
    "plt.plot(d['time'][k], c[:, aper].sum(axis=1)[k])"
   ]
